I'm happy to chat with you, but I think there's been a misunderstanding! As a conversational AI, I don't have personal experiences or interactions with pets, so I don't have information about Luna's activities or preferences.

I'm here to provide information, answer questions, and engage in conversation, but I don't have personal experiences or direct interactions with the physical world. I exist solely as a digital entity, so I don't have the ability to observe or interact with pets or their toys.

However, I'm always happy to help with questions or topics related to pets, pet care, or any other subject you'd like to discuss!
